Package: ecomsUDG.Raccess
Depends: downscaleR.java, downscaleR, R(>= 3.0.0)
Imports: utils, abind, RCurl
Suggests: sp
Type: Package
Title: The R interface for accessing the ECOMS User Data Gateway
Version: 2.2-5
Date: 06 Sep 2014
Authors@R: as.person(c(
    "Joaquin Bedia <bediaj@unican.es> [aut, cre]",
    "Max Tuni <max@predictia.es> [ctb]",
    "Antonio Cofino <antonio.cofino@unican.es> [ctb]",
    "Santander Meteorology Group <http://meteo.unican.es> [cph]"))
BugReports: https://github.com/SantanderMetGroup/ecomsUDG.Raccess/issues
URL: http://meteo.unican.es/ecoms-udg
Description: This package enables homogenized, user-friendly access to hindcast
 and other climate databases remotely stored at the ECOMS User Data Gateway, 
 allowing the retrieval of manageable dimensional slices from large climate datasets.
 The use of this package requires prior registration in the ECOMS-UDG
 (go to <http://meteo.unican.es/ecoms-udg/DataServer/Registration>).
License: GPL (>= 3)
